    "aboutus_founder_LAweay": {
      "type": "aboutus-founder",
      "name": "Meet the Mind Behind",
      "settings": {
        "bg_image": "shopify://shop_images/img2.png",
        "founder_image": "shopify://shop_images/Founder_image_1_bb624e15-6460-476a-99bf-dfac0dc143fa.png",
        "heading": "MEET THE MIND BEHIND <br> MY BEST LIFE™",
        "text": "<p><strong>As a doctor deeply invested in health and wellness, I’ve witnessed firsthand the gap between market offerings and what true wellness demands. I believe wellness should be accessible, transparent, and truly effective. My Best Life</strong>™<strong> was born out of a passion for uncovering natural, science-backed solutions that deliver real results.</strong></p><p><strong>This isn’t just a business — it’s a personal commitment to integrity, innovation, and transparency. With decades of experience across healthcare, pharmaceuticals, and nutraceuticals, I am dedicated to building a transformative brand that redefines preventive health.</strong></p><p><strong>Our mission is simple: to empower everyday wellness with pure, effective ingredients. My vision is to help you live a longer, healthier, and more vibrant life — every single day.</strong></p>",
        "author": "–Dr. Vikram Shetty"
      }
    },
    "testimonial_slider_p6zQY8": {
      "type": "testimonial-slider",
      "blocks": {
        "testimonial_WD84UM": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "stars": 5,
            "user_image": "shopify://shop_images/142defe2dca0a9b7ef8f1ef8fce521516898713b.png",
            "name-person": "Shantivardhini",
            "position": "",
            "stars_image": "shopify://shop_images/Golden-5-Star-Rating-PNG.png",
            "head_text": "My Skin Finally Looks Alive Again",
            "review_text": "I’ve struggled with dull, tired-looking skin for years, and nothing topical really helped. After about 9 weeks of Melt n Glo, my skin actually looks awake. The glutathione + vitamin C combo is doing something magical, my tone is more even, and I can skip foundation some days. The best part is it melts in your mouth, so I never forget to take it",
            "name": "MELT N GLO CUSTOMER",
            "date": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_d9KeHd": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "stars": 5,
            "user_image": "shopify://shop_images/142defe2dca0a9b7ef8f1ef8fce521516898713b.png",
            "name-person": "Shimmi Damodaran",
            "position": "",
            "stars_image": "shopify://shop_images/Golden-5-Star-Rating-PNG_031b84d3-2439-465c-af33-310f6564f546.png",
            "head_text": "Pigmentation Patches Are Fading",
            "review_text": "I have stubborn hyperpigmentation on my cheeks from old acne marks, and I’ve been using Melt n Glo for 2 months now. The glutathione with selenium and zinc seems to be working, my spots are lighter and my skin looks brighter overall. Took off one star because I wish it came in more flavors, but the results are worth it",
            "name": "MELT N GLO CUSTOMER",
            "date": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_j4BCHE": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "stars": 5,
            "user_image": "shopify://shop_images/142defe2dca0a9b7ef8f1ef8fce521516898713b.png",
            "name-person": "Pooja Hemanth",
            "position": "",
            "stars_image": "shopify://shop_images/Golden-5-Star-Rating-PNG.png",
            "head_text": "No more flaky patches",
            "review_text": "Living in an air-conditioned office all day made my skin so dry that even expensive creams didn’t help. NutraDew works differently, ceramides repair the skin barrier while hyaluronic acid holds on to the moisture. Now my skin stays smooth and hydrated all day, and my makeup doesn’t crack around my eyes",
            "name": "NUTRADEW CUSTOMER",
            "date": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_JdAfpT": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "stars": 5,
            "user_image": "shopify://shop_images/142defe2dca0a9b7ef8f1ef8fce521516898713b.png",
            "name-person": "Renuka Ravi",
            "position": "",
            "stars_image": "shopify://shop_images/Golden-5-Star-Rating-PNG_031b84d3-2439-465c-af33-310f6564f546.png",
            "head_text": "From dull to dewy",
            "review_text": "I’m in my 40s and have always struggled with rough texture and dehydration lines. After 8 weeks on NutraDew, my skin feels more supple, and I wake up looking fresher. It’s not a miracle overnight fix, but the hydration boost is real. Four stars only because I wish it came in a bigger pack!",
            "name": "NUTRADEW CUSTOMER",
            "date": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_FDfpLC": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "stars": 5,
            "user_image": "shopify://shop_images/142defe2dca0a9b7ef8f1ef8fce521516898713b.png",
            "name-person": "Vinitha Shetty",
            "position": "",
            "stars_image": "shopify://shop_images/Golden-5-Star-Rating-PNG.png",
            "head_text": "Noticeable Brightness in Just Weeks",
            "review_text": "I was skeptical about supplements, but I researched glutathione and vitamins C & E before trying this. Within 10 weeks, my uneven skin tone started evening out. Friends keep asking what skincare I’m using, but the only thing I changed was adding Melt n Glo to my routine. Love that it’s quick, tasty, and doesn’t feel like I’m taking “medicine.”",
            "name": "MELT N GLO CUSTOMER",
            "date": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_bejPbe": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "stars": 5,
            "user_image": "shopify://shop_images/142defe2dca0a9b7ef8f1ef8fce521516898713b.png",
            "name-person": "Revathi S.",
            "position": "",
            "stars_image": "shopify://shop_images/Golden-5-Star-Rating-PNG.png",
            "head_text": "Fine lines fading",
            "review_text": "Two months in, and I can see a visible difference in my crow’s feet and forehead lines. My skin feels bouncier and looks healthier overall. I’m convinced the ceramide-hyaluronic acid combo is the secret. This is the first supplement I’ve ever reordered without hesitation",
            "name": "NUTRADEW CUSTOMER",
            "date": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_YXtjG3": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "stars": 5,
            "user_image": "shopify://shop_images/142defe2dca0a9b7ef8f1ef8fce521516898713b.png",
            "name-person": "Sameeth K",
            "position": "",
            "stars_image": "shopify://shop_images/Golden-5-Star-Rating-PNG.png",
            "head_text": "Confidence Without Makeup",
            "review_text": "I’ve had uneven skin tone for years, and it always made me pile on concealer. After using Melt n Glo for 3 months, I’ve been going makeup-free more often. My skin looks more even, has a natural glow, and feels smoother. The mix of glutathione, pomegranate extract, vitamin E, and zinc really seems to be nourishing from the inside",
            "name": "MELT N GLO CUSTOMER",
            "date": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_Xa9aX8": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "stars": 5,
            "user_image": "shopify://shop_images/142defe2dca0a9b7ef8f1ef8fce521516898713b.png",
            "name-person": "Nandini Gowda",
            "position": "",
            "stars_image": "shopify://shop_images/Golden-5-Star-Rating-PNG.png",
            "head_text": "My Go-To for Dull Skin Days",
            "review_text": "I work long hours, and my skin used to look flat and lifeless. Melt n Glo has been a game-changer. The combination of glutathione, marigold extract, vitamin C, and selenium is giving me brightness I didn’t know I could get. Even my hyperpigmentation marks are less noticeable now. It’s so easy to take daily, no pills or mixing powders",
            "name": "MELT N GLO CUSTOMER",
            "date": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_CMWB8z": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "stars": 5,
            "user_image": "shopify://shop_images/142defe2dca0a9b7ef8f1ef8fce521516898713b.png",
            "name-person": "Rajiv Rajan",
            "position": "",
            "stars_image": "shopify://shop_images/Golden-5-Star-Rating-PNG.png",
            "head_text": "Didn’t Think This Was for Guys, but…",
            "review_text": "I’ll be honest, I bought Melt n Glo because my wife kept telling me my skin looked “tired” and uneven. I wasn’t expecting much, but after about 10 weeks, even I can see the difference. My face looks fresher, the tan patches from old sun damage have lightened, and I don’t look like I’ve been pulling all-nighters anymore. Plus, it’s super easy to take, no pills, just melts on your tongue. I’m sticking with it",
            "name": "MELT N GLO CUSTOMER",
            "date": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_9fyQTB": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "stars": 5,
            "user_image": "shopify://shop_images/142defe2dca0a9b7ef8f1ef8fce521516898713b.png",
            "name-person": "Archana Chopra",
            "position": "",
            "stars_image": "shopify://shop_images/Golden-5-Star-Rating-PNG.png",
            "head_text": "My skin drinks this up",
            "review_text": "I’ve had dry, tight skin for years, no matter how much moisturizer I used. NutraDew’s ceramides and hyaluronic acid combo is a game-changer. Within 6 weeks, my skin feels hydrated from the inside out. The flakiness around my nose is gone, and my cheeks feel soft all day. Even my smile lines look less noticeable.",
            "name": "NUTRADEW CUSTOMER",
            "date": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_w7tpPH": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "stars": 5,
            "user_image": "shopify://shop_images/142defe2dca0a9b7ef8f1ef8fce521516898713b.png",
            "name-person": "Renuka Ravi",
            "position": "",
            "stars_image": "shopify://shop_images/Golden-5-Star-Rating-PNG.png",
            "head_text": "Wrinkles? Softer now",
            "review_text": "I started NutraDew mainly for dryness, but I’m surprised how much smoother my fine lines look. The hyaluronic acid really plumps up my skin, and the ceramides seem to lock in that moisture. People at work keep asking if I’ve changed my skincare, but nope, just this little tablet every day.",
            "name": "NUTRADEW CUSTOMER",
            "date": ""
          }
        }
      },
